com.company

Class Stackotaire

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.company.Stackotaire

  • public class Stackotaire
extends java.lang.Object
    first, it initializes the game with 52 different card and put them into different stack. Then, it prompts the user for further action draw - to draw the card from stock to waste restart - to restart the game quit - to terminate the game move - to move a card from one stock to another (takes 2 arguments, the stack moving from and the stack moving to ) moveN - to move more than 1 card from one to another (takes 3 arguments, the stack moving from, the stack moving to and how many cards are moving) undo - to undo previous step
